info.description:
### Description
This API powers Sealed League, a platform for running sealed deck leagues,
tracking card pools, and organizing tournaments.

Use the API documentation below to explore endpoints and integrations.

### Table of Contents
*(links only work for ReDoc, not for Swagger UI)*

- [Auth](#tag/Auth)

- [Clubs](#tag/Clubs)

- [Courts](#tag/Courts)

- [Internals](#tag/Internals)

- [League](#tag/League)

- [League Cards](#tag/League-Cards)

- [Matches](#tag/Matches)

- [Players](#tag/Players)

- [Rankings](#tag/Rankings)

- [Rounds](#tag/Rounds)

- [Stage Items](#tag/Stage-Items)

- [Stage Item Inputs](#tag/Stage-Item-Inputs)

- [Stages](#tag/Stages)

- [Teams](#tag/Teams)

- [Tournaments](#tag/Tournaments)

- [Users](#tag/Users)
